Package: create-repo-auto
Version: 1.3.0
Section: utils
Priority: optional
Architecture: all
Essential: no
Maintainer: justrunme <justrunme@gmail>
Depends: bash, git, curl, jq
Description: create-repo - A CLI tool for rapid and automated initialization, publication, and synchronization of Git repositories (GitHub/GitLab/Bitbucket), with automatic tracking via cron or launchd.
 This package installs:
  - create-repo (main CLI script)
  - update-all (auto-sync script)
  - Supports interactive mode, auto-update, and more.
